{"tid":1872150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我和會員降囝（牙降）不相見已一年餘了","createTime":"2020-02-10T02:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T12:38:30.000Z","uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"efd8c26feb069f0cf4f2262e23405d21d8022ef0","tid":1872150,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:16:04.000Z","msg":"我與牙降不相見已一年餘了，我最不能忘記的是他的膠post。<br />\n<br />\n那年冬天，izone死了，金彩元的空降也踢爆了，正是禍不單行的日子。<br />\n我從手機打開連登，打算狙擊我老死牙降玩遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n到進入進入連登搜尋著降囝，看見滿院狼藉的負皮膠post，又想起彩演，不禁簌簌地流下眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n牙降退出連登前說：&ldquo;事已如此，不必難過，好在天無絕人之路！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e7bcd2450bab2ea3c199f3791eae56410f82d7d9","tid":1872150,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:18:38.000Z","msg":"你條臭雞想降囝埋你單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"1d2a31e8b235fa022db4b26c079176779c2ab40c","tid":1872150,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔記得左哩個人"},{"pid":"9375333df686699fbc0dc30f4ef751515e3c2608","tid":1872150,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"03e4f9f61643b1cf8bc5689f07077e6f9b4d5517","tid":1872150,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"\\|/"},{"pid":"e864faded144ee431c87ea0ac4b142540c733e20","tid":1872150,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"\\|/"},{"pid":"ec778db309f593828515488406f71df451a69c10","tid":1872150,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"大家點睇宋亨俊，牙喊?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1148943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1148943</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n百事真係比狗飲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http